context: Adenoidectomy. Adenoid hypertrophy. The McIvor mouth gag was placed in the oral cavity and the tongue depressor applied.   (Medical Transcription Sample Report)
Adenoid hypertrophy. The McIvor mouth gag was placed in the oral cavity and the tongue depressor applied.   (Medical Transcription Sample Report)
The patient was taken to the operating room and prepped and draped in the usual fashion after induction of general endotracheal anesthesia
The nasopharynx was inspected with the laryngeal mirror. Serial passages of the curettes were utilized to remove the nasopharyngeal tissue,
The McIvor was reopened, packs removed, and the bleeding was controlled with the suction Bovie unit.
The patient tolerated the procedure well and left the operating room in good condition.
